name: The Walking Dead: Season Two - Episode 5: No Going Back
name_original: The Walking Dead: Season Two - Episode 5: No Going Back
description:
The Walking Dead: Season Two - Episode 5: No Going Back is an action-adventure game developed by Telltale Games. It was originally released in 2014. It was published by Telltale Games. Most rawgers rated the game as "Recommended".
You can play The Walking Dead: Season Two - Episode 5: No Going Back on PC, iOS, Android and Xbox 360.
